The paper deals with the problem of text extraction from PDF images, which involves techniques related to computer vision (CV) and information retrieval (IR). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning (DL) techniques for text extraction. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of natural language processing (NLP) techniques for automatic annotation and indexing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (CL) and machine learning (LG). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CV and cs.IR, followed by cs.DL, cs.CL, and cs.LG.
